{"tid":2053543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國朋友: 巴基斯坦確診多4734宗新型肺炎　累計逾9萬宗","createTime":"2020-06-06T11:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T11:04:45.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6348c4464609252b9f97a0d7550e66e323afd2b6","tid":2053543,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>巴基斯坦衛生部表示，新增新型肺炎病例4734宗，累計確診9萬3千宗，新增97宗死亡，累計1935人死。</strong><br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦東部旁遮普省和南部信德省疫情較為嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，巴基斯坦政府表示，將採取包括罰款在內的嚴格措施，確保復工復產的各行業和民眾，遵守政府制定的各項防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530561-20200606.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530561-20200606.htm&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=d1a3a28a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530561-20200606.htm&h=1bf2a7ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530561-20200606.htm</a>"}]}